WITH december_sne AS
  (SELECT oid,
          firstmjd,
          lastmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   WHERE firstmjd >= '2022-12-01'::DATE
     AND firstmjd < '2023-09-01'::DATE -- Additional conditions based on the user request
),
     september_sne AS
  (SELECT oid,
          firstmjd,
          lastmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   WHERE firstmjd >= '2023-09-01'::DATE
     AND firstmjd <= '2023-09-30'::DATE -- Additional conditions based on the user request
)
SELECT s.classifier_name,
       s.probability,
       d.firstmjd,
       d.lastmjd,
       o.oid
FROM december_sne d
JOIN september_sne s ON d.oid = s.oid;

WITH ranked_objects AS
  (SELECT oid,
          probability,
          ranking,
          CASE
              WHEN class_name = 'SNIa' THEN 'SNIa_prob'
              WHEN class_name = 'CV/Nova' THEN 'CV_prob'
              ELSE 'Unknown_prob'
          END AS class_name
   FROM probability
   WHERE classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND class_name IN ('SNIa',
                        'CV/Nova')
     AND ranking IN (1,
                     2) )
SELECT oid,
       COALESCE(SNIa_prob, 0) AS SN_prob,
       COALESCE(CV_prob, 0) AS CV_prob
FROM ranked_objects
WHERE SNIa_prob IS NOT NULL
  OR CV_prob IS NOT NULL;

WITH ranked_probs AS
  (SELECT p.oid,
          p.classifier_name,
          p.probability,
          p.ranking,
          CASE
              WHEN p.class_name = 'SNIa' THEN 1
              ELSE 2
          END AS cv_or_sni_rank
   FROM probability p
   INNER JOIN
     (SELECT oid,
             MAX(ranking) AS max_ranking
      FROM probability
      GROUP BY oid) m ON p.oid = m.oid
   AND p.ranking = m.max_ranking
   WHERE p.class_name IN ('SNIa',
                          'CV/Nova')
     AND p.ranking IN (1,
                       2) ),
     prob_classes AS
  (SELECT oid,
          CASE
              WHEN cv_or_sni_rank = 1 THEN 'SN_prob'
              ELSE 'CV_prob'
          END AS prob_class,
          probability AS prob
   FROM ranked_probs)
SELECT oid,
       prob_class,
       prob
FROM prob_classes;

   JOIN light_curve_detections lfd ON o.oid = lfd.oid)

FROM object_with_stats
WHERE o.oid IN

WITH source_info AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT oid,
                   ra, dec
   FROM probability
   WHERE classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND class_name IN ('AGN',
                        'QSO',
                        'Blazar')
     AND ndet >= 40
     AND julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) - julianday(firstMJD) >= 200 ),
     filtered_sources AS
  (SELECT oid,
          ra, dec, SUM(ndet) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS total_detections,
                                  MIN(julianday(firstMJD + deltajd)) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS min_first_mjd,
                                                                          MAX(julianday(firstMJD + deltajd)) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS max_last_mjd
   FROM source_info),
     probabilities_per_source AS
  (SELECT s.oid,
          s.ra,
          s.dec,
          COUNT(*) FILTER (
                           WHERE p.probability > 0.8) AS blazar_count,
          COUNT(*) FILTER (
                           WHERE p.probability > 0.95) AS agn_qso_count,
          AVG(p.probability) FILTER (
                                     WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier') AS avg_prob
   FROM filtered_sources f
   INNER JOIN source_info s ON f.oid = s.oid
   LEFT JOIN probability p ON f.oid = p.oid
   GROUP BY s.oid,
            s.ra,
            s.dec),
     combined_probs AS
  (SELECT oid,
          ra, dec, total_detections,
                   min_first_mjd,
                   max_last_mjd,
                   CASE
                       WHEN blazar_count IS NOT NULL THEN blazar_count
                       ELSE 0
                   END AS blazar_prob,
                   CASE
                       WHEN agn_qso_count IS NOT NULL THEN agn_qso_count
                       ELSE 0
                   END AS agn_qso_prob,
                   AVG(avg_prob) OVER () AS combined_avg_prob
   FROM probabilities_per_source)
SELECT oid,
       ra, dec, total_detections,
                min_first_mjd,
                max_last_mjd,
                CASE
                    WHEN blazar_prob > 0 THEN blazar_prob
                    ELSE 0
                END AS blazar_prob,
                CASE
                    WHEN agn_qso_prob > 0 THEN agn_qso_prob
                    ELSE 0
                END AS agn_qso_prob,
                CASE
                    WHEN combined_avg_prob > 0 THEN combined_avg_prob
                    ELSE 0
                END AS combined_avg_prob
FROM combined_probs
WHERE (blazar_prob > 0
       OR agn_qso_prob > 0
       OR combined_avg_prob > 0);

WITH source_info AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT oid,
                   ra, dec
   FROM probability
   WHERE classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND class_name IN ('AGN',
                        'QSO',
                        'Blazar')
     AND ndet >= 40
     AND julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) - julianday(firstMJD) > 200 ),
     filtered_sources AS
  (SELECT oid,
          ra, dec, SUM(ndet) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS total_detections,
                                  MIN(julianday(firstMJD + deltajd)) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS min_first_mjd,
                                                                          MAX(julianday(firstMJD + deltajd)) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS max_last_mjd
   FROM
     (SELECT oid,
             ra, dec, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS ndet,
                                    julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) AS firstMJD,
                                    julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) - julianday(firstMJD) AS deltajd
      FROM
        (SELECT oid,
                ra, dec, COUNT(*) AS ndet,
                         julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) AS firstMJD,
                         julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) - julianday(firstMJD) AS deltajd
         FROM
           (SELECT p.oid,
                   p.ra,
                   p.dec,
                   COUNT(*) AS ndet,
                   julianday(p.firstMJD + p.deltajd) AS firstMJD,
                   julianday(p.firstMJD + p.deltajd) - julianday(p.firstMJD) AS deltajd
            FROM probability p
            INNER JOIN source_info s ON p.oid = s.oid
            GROUP BY p.oid,
                     p.ra,
                     p.dec,
                     p.ndet,
                     p.firstMJD,
                     p.deltajd)
         WHERE ndet >= 40
           AND julianday(firstMJD + deltajd) - julianday(firstMJD) > 200 ) t) t),
     mean_values AS
  (SELECT oid,
          ra, dec, total_detections,
                   min_first_mjd,
                   max_last_mjd,
                   AVG(ndet) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS avg_ndet,
                                  AVG(deltajd) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS avg_deltajd,
                                                    SUM(probability) OVER (PARTITION BY oid) AS sum_prob,
                                                                          COUNT(DISTINCT CASE
                                                                                             WHEN probability > 0.8 THEN oid
                                                                                             ELSE NULL
                                                                                         END) FILTER (
                                                                                                      WHERE probability > 0.8) AS blazar_count,
                                                                          COUNT(DISTINCT CASE
                                                                                             WHEN probability > 0.95 THEN oid
                                                                                             ELSE NULL
                                                                                         END) FILTER (
                                                                                                      WHERE probability > 0.95) AS agn_qso_count
   FROM filtered_sources)
SELECT oid,
       ra, dec, total_detections,
                min_first_mjd,
                max_last_mjd,
                avg_ndet,
                avg_deltajd,
                sum_prob,
                blazar_count,
                agn_qso_count,
                mean_prob AS mean_prob,
                mean_ranking AS mean_ranking
FROM
  (SELECT oid,
          ra, dec, total_detections,
                   min_first_mjd,
                   max_last_mjd,
                   avg_ndet,
                   avg_deltajd,
                   sum_prob,
                   blazar_count,
                   agn_qso_count,
                   probability AS mean_prob,
                   ranking AS mean_ranking
   FROM mean_values
   WHERE probability <= 0.8
     OR probability BETWEEN 0.8 AND 0.95
   UNION ALL SELECT oid,
                    ra, dec, total_detections,
                             min_first_mjd,
                             max_last_mjd,
                             avg_ndet,
                             avg_deltajd,
                             sum_prob,
                             blazar_count,
                             agn_qso_count,
                             probability AS mean_prob,
                             ranking AS mean_ranking
   FROM mean_values
   WHERE probability > 0.8
     AND probability < 0.95 ) subq
ORDER BY oid;

WITH periodic_objects AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          o.possibility,
          f.value,
          f.name,
          f.fid,
          fv.version
   FROM OBJECT o
   JOIN feature f ON o.oid = f.oid
   JOIN feature_version fv ON f.version = fv.version
   WHERE o.stellar = FALSE
     AND o.corrected = TRUE
     AND o.ndet > 0
     AND f.name IN ('Periodicity',
                    'Variability')
     AND f.value BETWEEN 3 AND 10
     AND f.value * f.value / 0.5 >= 0.5 ),
     filtered_objects AS
  (SELECT po.oid,
          po.possibility,
          po.value,
          po.name,
          po.fid,
          po.version
   FROM periodic_objects po
   WHERE po.possibility > 0.7 )
SELECT DISTINCT o.oid,
                o.possibility,
                f.value,
                f.name,
                f.fid,
                fv.version
FROM filtered_objects fo
JOIN OBJECT o ON fo.oid = o.oid
JOIN feature f ON fo.oid = f.oid
JOIN feature_version fv ON f.version = fv.version
ORDER BY fo.possibility DESC;

          firstmjd
   FROM OBJECT

       l.classifier_name,
       f.value

JOIN
  (SELECT oid,
          MAX(firstmjd) AS max_firstmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   GROUP BY oid) o_max ON o.oid = o_max.oid

  (SELECT oid,
          MIN(firstmjd) AS min_firstmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   GROUP BY oid) o_min ON o.oid = o_min.oid
AND o.lastmjd = o_min.min_firstmjd

  (SELECT oid,
          MAX(ndet) AS max_ndet
   FROM OBJECT

  (SELECT oid,
          MIN(ndet) AS min_ndet
   FROM OBJECT
   GROUP BY oid) o_min_ndet ON o.oid = o_min_ndet.oid
AND o.ndet = o_min_ndet.min_ndet

  (SELECT oid,
          firstmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   WHERE firstmjd BETWEEN 59976 AND 59978 )
SELECT o.oid,
       f.name,
       l.classifier_name,
       f.value
FROM earliest_detection e
JOIN OBJECT o ON e.oid = o.oid
JOIN feature f ON o.oid = f.oid
JOIN
  (SELECT classifier_name,
          MAX(firstmjd) AS max_firstmjd
   FROM OBJECT
   GROUP BY classifier_name) lc ON e.oid = lc.oid

WHERE lc.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier';

2.sql_query:
WITH filtered_detections AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT d.candid,
                   d.mjd,
                   d.fid,
                   d.pid,
                   d.diffmaglim,
                   d.isdiffpos,
                   d.nid,
                   d.ra,
                   d.dec,
                   d.magpsf,
                   d.sigmagpsf,
                   d.magap,
                   d.sigmagap,
                   d.distnr,
                   d.rb,
                   d.rbversion,
                   d.drb,
                   d.drbversion,
                   d.magapbig,
                   d.sigmagapbig,
                   d.rfid,
                   d.magpsf_corr,
                   d.sigmagpsf_corr,
                   d.sigmagpsf_corr_ext,
                   d.corrected,
                   d.dubious,
                   d.parent_candid,
                   d.has_stamp,
                   d.step_id_corr
   FROM detection d
   INNER JOIN probability p ON d.oid = p.oid
   AND p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
   AND p.classifier_version = 'v1.0'
   WHERE p.probability > 0.6
     AND p.ranking = 1
     AND d.firstmjd BETWEEN 58484 AND 59944
     AND d.ndet > 30
     AND d.pid IN (1,
                   2)
     AND d.magpsf_corr < 0.5
     AND d.sigmagpsf_corr < 0.5
     AND d.sigmagpsf_corr_ext < 0.5 ),
     object_with_time_and_band AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          o.firstmjd,
          o.lastmjd,
          o.deltajd,
          o.ndethist,
          o.ncovhist,
          o.mjdstarthist,
          o.mjdendhist,
          o.correction,
          o.stellar,
          o.ndet,
          o.g_r_max,
          o.g_r_max_corr,
          o.g_r_mean,
          o.g_r_mean_corr,
          o.meanra,
          o.meandec,
          o.sigmara,
          o.sigmadec,
          o.step_id_corr,
          o.diffpos,
          o.reference_change,
          pd.f_id
   FROM OBJECT o
   JOIN filtered_detections fd ON o.oid = fd.oid)
SELECT *
FROM object_with_time_and_band;

   FROM OBJECT

WITH ztf_objects AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT o.oid,
                   d.candid
   FROM detection d
   INNER JOIN OBJECT o ON d.oid = o.oid
   WHERE d.isdiffpos = 1
     AND d.mjd - d.last_mjd_before_fid > 1 ),
     ztf_with_features AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          f.name,
          f.value,
          f.fid,
          p.classifier_version,
          p.classifier_name,
          p.probability
   FROM ztf_objects zo
   INNER JOIN feature f ON zo.oid = f.oid
   AND f.version = 'v1'
   INNER JOIN probability p ON zo.oid = p.oid
   AND p.ranking = 1
   WHERE f.name = 'LinearTrend'
     AND f.value > 5 ),
     ztf_light_curve_data AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          lfc.classifier_version,
          lfc.classifier_name,
          lfc.probability
   FROM ztf_objects zo
   INNER JOIN detection d ON zo.candid = d.candid
   INNER JOIN detection lfc ON d.pid = lfc.pid
   AND d.nid = lfc.nid
   WHERE lfc.probability IS NOT NULL )
SELECT zo.oid,
       COUNT(*) OVER () AS num_detections,
                     lfc.classifier_version,
                     lfc.classifier_name,
                     lfc.probability,
                     f.value,
                     f.fid
FROM ztf_objects zo
JOIN ztf_with_features zwf ON zo.oid = zwf.oid
JOIN ztf_light_curve_data zlcd ON zo.oid = zlcd.oid
WHERE zwf.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
  AND zwf.probability >= zwf.probability * 0.9
ORDER BY zwf.probability DESC,
         zwf.ranking ASC
LIMIT 10;

WITH ztf_objects AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          p.probability
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.classifier_version = 'hierarchical_rf_1.1.0'
     AND p.probability > 0.7 ),
     ps1_sources AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT s.oid AS ps1_oid,
                   s.ra,
                   s.dec
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.classifier_version = 'hierarchical_rf_1.1.0'
     AND p.probability > 0.7
     AND p.ranking = 1 ),
     nearest_ps1 AS
  (SELECT ps1_oid,
          MIN(distance) AS min_distance
   FROM ps1_sources
   GROUP BY ps1_oid),
     ztf_candidates AS
  (SELECT o.candidate,
          o.filter,
          e.reduced_chi_sq,
          e.star_gal_score_se,
          ps1.sgrs_score,
          ps1.distance
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   INNER JOIN ztf_objects zo ON o.oid = zo.oid
   INNER JOIN ps1_sources ps1 ON o.oid = ps1.ps1_oid
   INNER JOIN nearest_ps1 np ON o.oid = np.ps1_oid
   INNER JOIN ztf_objects zo2 ON o.oid = zo2.oid
   INNER JOIN OBJECT e ON o.oid = e.oid
   WHERE zo.probability > 0.7
     AND zo2.probability > 0.7
     AND zo.min_distance < 2
     AND zo2.min_distance < 2
     AND ABS(ps1.sgrs_score - e.star_gal_score_se) < 0.5 )
SELECT zo.oid,
       zo.probability,
       oc.candidate,
       oc.filter,
       e.reduced_chi_sq,
       e.star_gal_score_se,
       ps1.sgrs_score,
       ps1.distance
FROM ztf_candidates oc
JOIN ztf_objects zo ON oc.oid = zo.oid
JOIN nearest_ps1 np ON oc.oid = np.ps1_oid;

WITH ztf_objects AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          p.probability
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.classifier_version = 'hierarchical_rf_1.1.0'
     AND p.probability > 0.7 ),
     ps1_sources AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT s.oid AS ps1_oid,
                   s.ra,
                   s.dec
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.classifier_version = 'hierarchical_rf_1.1.0'
     AND p.probability > 0.7
     AND p.ranking = 1 ),
     nearest_ps1 AS
  (SELECT ps1_oid,
          MIN(distance) AS min_distance
   FROM ps1_sources
   GROUP BY ps1_oid),
     ztf_candidates AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          o.candidate,
          o.filter,
          o.reduced_chi_square,
          s.score AS se_score,
          ps1_score,
          ps1.distance AS ps1_distance
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   INNER JOIN ps1_sources ps1 ON o.oid = ps1.ps1_oid
   INNER JOIN nearest_ps1 nps1 ON o.oid = nps1.ps1_oid
   INNER JOIN
     (SELECT oid,
             MAX(reduced_chi_square) AS max_reduced_chi_square
      FROM OBJECT
      GROUP BY oid) max_chisq ON o.oid = max_chisq.oid
   INNER JOIN
     (SELECT oid,
             MAX(score) AS max_se_score
      FROM OBJECT
      GROUP BY oid) max_se ON o.oid = max_se.oid
   INNER JOIN
     (SELECT oid,
             MAX(ps1_score) AS max_ps1_score
      FROM OBJECT
      GROUP BY oid) max_ps1 ON o.oid = max_ps1.oid
   INNER JOIN
     (SELECT oid,
             MAX(distance) AS max_ps1_distance
      FROM OBJECT
      GROUP BY oid) max_ps1_dist ON o.oid = max_ps1_dist.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.classifier_version = 'hierarchical_rf_1.1.0'
     AND p.probability > 0.7
     AND p.ranking = 1
     AND ABS(p.se_score - ps1_score) < 0.5 )
SELECT TOP 50 z.object.oid,
           z.object.probability,
           z.t_candidate.oid AS t_candidate_oid,
           z.t_candidate.filter AS t_candidate_filter,
           z.t_candidate.reduced_chi_square AS t_candidate_reduced_chi_square,
           z.t_candidate.se_score AS t_candidate_se_score,
           z.t_candidate.ps1_score AS t_candidate_ps1_score,
           z.t_candidate.ps1_distance AS t_candidate_ps1_distance
FROM ztf_objects z
JOIN ztf_candidates c ON z.oid = c.oid
ORDER BY z.object.probability DESC;

WITH obj_coords AS
  (SELECT oid AS id,
          ra AS obj_ra,
          dec AS obj_dec
   FROM OBJECT
   WHERE oid = 'id_1' ),
     allwise_coords AS
  (SELECT oid_catalog AS id,
          ra AS obj_ra,
          dec AS obj_dec
   FROM allwise
   WHERE ra = 132.961
     AND dec = 41.397 ),
     search_radius AS
  (SELECT CASE
              WHEN obj_ra - obj_coords.obj_ra < 0 THEN obj_ra - obj_coords.obj_ra
              ELSE obj_coords.obj_ra - obj_ra
          END AS min_diff,
          CASE
              WHEN obj_ra - obj_coords.obj_ra > 0 THEN obj_ra - obj_coords.obj_ra
              ELSE obj_coords.obj_ra - obj_ra
          END AS max_diff
   FROM obj_coords),
     allwise_objects AS
  (SELECT oid_catalog AS id,
          ra AS obj_ra,
          dec AS obj_dec,
          w1mpro AS w1_mag,
          w1sigmpro AS w1_uncertainty
   FROM allwise
   WHERE ra BETWEEN obj_coords.min_diff AND obj_coords.max_diff )
SELECT o.id AS id,
       a.obj_ra AS obj_ra,
       a.obj_dec AS obj_dec,
       s.r_deg AS r_deg
FROM obj_coords o
JOIN allwise_objects a ON abs(o.obj_ra - a.obj_ra) <= 5
OR abs(o.obj_dec - a.obj_dec) <= 5
JOIN search_radius s ON s.min_diff <= abs(o.obj_ra - a.obj_ra)
AND s.max_diff >= abs(o.obj_ra - a.obj_ra)
ORDER BY o.id;

```SQL WITH ztf_objects AS
  (SELECT DISTINCT t1.oid,
                   COUNT(*) AS num_detections
   FROM gaia_ztf t1
   WHERE CAST(t1.maggaia AS REAL) < 1
     AND CAST(t1.maggaiabright AS REAL) < 1
   GROUP BY t1.oid)
SELECT z.object.oid AS ztf_identifier,
       z.num_detections,
       julianday(z.object.min_g_mag) - julianday(z.object.min_r_mag) AS diff_min_g_r_magnitudes,
       z.feature.w1_w2 AS w1_w2,
       fv.version AS feature_version
FROM gaia_ztf z
JOIN
  (SELECT oid,
          min(g_band_mag) AS min_g_mag,
          max(r_band_mag) AS max_r_mag
   FROM gaia_ztf
   GROUP BY oid) z_object ON z.object.oid = z_object.oid
JOIN
  (SELECT oid,
          min(g_band_mag) AS min_g_mag,
          max(r_band_mag) AS max_r_mag
   FROM gaia_ztf
   GROUP BY oid) z_object2 ON z.object.oid = z_object2.oid
